	oors open at 5:30. Trivia starts at 6:30!all ages til 8pm!Tables are first
	 come first serve. \\*\\*PRIZES\\*\\*The RAISED BY TV gang has put togethe
	r some killer prize packages. Teams of 1-5 are welcome. Prizes for 1st\, 2
	nd\, t have to be good at trivia just come on down to relive some Scranton
	 shenanigans with us. \\*\\*FOOD & DRINKS\\*\\*The Clock-Out has bar and f
	ull Stevies Famous Pizza food service\; one of the things that makes it ou
	r favorite place.The show is available on PeacockWe hope you can join RbyT
	V for a safe night of fun and brains.Brandon Ryan\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amc
	ity.com/events/#/details/raised-by-tv-events-presents-all-ages-the-office-
